+  - `PokerSolver::with_encoder_bytes(...)`
+  - `PokerSolver::with_encoder_file(...)`
+  - `PokerSolver::load_with_encoder_bytes(...)`
+  - `PokerSolver::load_with_encoder_file(...)`
